    c.column_0,
    SUM(CASE WHEN c.column_11 = '1' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS count,
    (SUM(CASE WHEN c.column_11 = '1' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*) * 100) AS percentage
FROM cards c
WHERE c.column_7 = 'Story Spotlight'
GROUP BY c.column_0
ORDER BY column_0;
